snippet.title: NBA 2K14 Next-Gen: OMG Trailer
snippet.description:
Experience the next-generation of NBA 2K14 for the first time in this brand new trailer. Can you feel it coming in the air tonight?

NBA 2K14 available at launch of the next gen consoles
For more information, LIKE us on Facebook:
http://2kgam.es/NBA2KFacebook

ESRB Rating: EVERYONE
